{{Quote|I tracked the known sources of Phrik and came across a selection of small moons in the Gromas system. It's probably not a coincidence that the Empire has a mining facility in that very system.|[[Jan Ors]]|<ref name="DF" />}}
The '''Gromas Mines''' were an [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Mining/Legends|mining]] facility located on the [[Moon/Legends|moon]] [[Gromas 16]]. It was built when the Empire cleaned the [[Gromas system/Legends|Gromas system]], in order to be a part of [[Rom Mohc]]'s [[Dark Trooper Project]] and supply it with [[phrikite]].<ref name="DF" />

[[Kyle Katarn]], having discovered a sample on [[Fest/Legends|Fest]], was led to infiltrate the facility, detonating the [[Reactor/Legends|reactor]] to destroy it. The Empire abandoned Gromas after Katarn's assault, leaving the skeleton of their base on Gromas 16.<ref name="DF" />

